00:06:51.070 --> 00:06:54.070
Ouais!

00:06:54.070 --> 00:06:56.580
Tu es si...! Tu es si...!

00:06:56.580 --> 00:06:57.950
Merci! Je suis sérieux!

00:06:59.710 --> 00:07:01.060
N-Non... Pas de problème... ! Ne me dérange pas, tu dois...

00:07:01.710 --> 00:07:03.460
Tu dois continuer, Luffy !

00:07:08.880 --> 00:07:13.550
Tu as raison!

00:07:14.970 --> 00:07:15.970
Merci!

00:07:15.970 --> 00:07:17.810
